snippet.title: Planet Zoo | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Build a world for wildlife in Planet Zoo, coming to PC in Fall 2019. 
From the developers of Planet Coaster and Zoo Tycoon comes the ultimate zoo sim, featuring authentic living animals who think, feel and explore the world you create around them. Experience a globe-trotting campaign or let your imagination run wild in the freedom of Sandbox mode. Create unique habitats and vast landscapes, make big decisions and meaningful choices, and nurture your animals as you construct and manage the world’s wildest zoos.

For more news and information about Planet Zoo:
Website: www.planetzoogame.com  
Facebook: facebook.com/PlanetZooGame    
Twitter: www.twitter.com/PlanetZooGame 
Instagram: @PlanetZooGame 

Planet Zoo © 2019 Frontier Developments plc. All rights reserved.

Music: “Gonna Build A Mountain”
Natalie Major featuring Young Mbazo.
Choir Director - Toya Delazy
Arranged by JJ Ipsen
Courtesy of TRO Essex Group, Downtown Music Publishing, and Raleigh Music Group
